Description:
create a heading on a page

Usage: create_metric_table_heading [-help]
                                   [-format {html excel text}] [-id <string>]
                                   -page <string> -title <string>
                                   [-type {fixed collapse}]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-format {html excel text}  # config for specified report_metric format
                           # (enum, optional)
-id <string>               # id for new heading (string, optional)
-page <string>             # page name to add heading to (string, required)
-title <string>            # title to be shown n heading (string, required)
-type {fixed collapse}     # type of heading element (fixed|collapse)
                           # (enum, optional)